<div1 type="trialAccount" id="t17510116-68">
               <interp inst="t17510116-68" type="collection" value="BAILEY"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17510116-68" type="year" value="1751"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17510116-68" type="uri" value="sessionsPapers/17510116"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17510116-68" type="date" value="17510116"></interp>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17510116-68-off316-c448" targOrder="Y" targets="t17510116-68-defend570 t17510116-68-off316 t17510116-68-verdict319"></join>
         
               <p>177. (M.) 
               
                  <persName id="t17510116-68-defend570" type="defendantName">
                     William 
                     Reynolds 
                  <interp inst="t17510116-68-defend570" type="surname" value="Reynolds"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17510116-68-defend570" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17510116-68-defend570" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , was indicted for <rs id="t17510116-68-off316" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17510116-68-off316" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17510116-68-off316" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing one hat, value 12 d. one wig, value 10 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17510116-68-victim572" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Pain 
                  <interp inst="t17510116-68-victim572" type="surname" value="Pain"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17510116-68-victim572" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17510116-68-victim572" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17510116-68-off316 t17510116-68-victim572"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17510116-68-cd317" type="crimeDate">Jan 2</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17510116-68-off316 t17510116-68-cd317"></join>. ++</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17510116-68-person573">
                  John 
                  Pain 
               <interp inst="t17510116-68-person573" type="surname" value="Pain"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17510116-68-person573" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17510116-68-person573" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live at <placeName id="t17510116-68-crimeloc318">the rising Sun and tobacco-roll in Fashion-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17510116-68-crimeloc318" type="placeName" value="the rising Sun and tobacco-roll in Fashion-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17510116-68-crimeloc318" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17510116-68-off316 t17510116-68-crimeloc318"></join>. On the 2d of Jan. my brother brought me home a new wig, my master paid the money for it, and carried it into the inward room, there were three or four gentlemen drinking there at that time; the wig was put on the table; this Reynolds the prisoner was in the room to wait upon the gentlemen, and about half an hour after they were gone, the prisoner went away; and in about half an hour after that, I missed my wig; the box was there in the room. We suspected he had the wig, we took him up upon suspicion; we taxed him with it, and he denied it, and just as he was committed he confessed it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I will not give the court any trouble, I did do it; I am 55 years of age, and I never was before a court in such a case in all my life before. I was in liquor.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17510116-68-verdict319" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17510116-68-verdict319" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty 10 d.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17510116-68-punish320" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17510116-68-punish320" type="punishmentCategory" value="corporal"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17510116-68-punish320" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="whipping"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17510116-68-defend570 t17510116-68-punish320"></join>
               
                     <note>[Whipping. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
            </div1>
